race.comment: JADE DIVISION (2) settled well back and failed to finish off when fifth over 1280m at Gilgandra. Assess on his good win two-back and expected to return to form in this easier contest. FRUIT OF DE VINE (9) finally got off the mark at start nine when a slick winner over 1200m at Queanbeyan. Confidence is high now and can go on with it today with Stiff's 3kg claim. BILLABONG ROSE (5) stripped fitter when a sharp winner as favourite over 1400m at Wellington. Looks up to this from the good gate and can figure in the finish. GAMOLINA (10) in need of the run first-up from the awkward gate when eighth over 1100m at Dubbo. Strips fitter and must be kept safe with a few gear changes.
